items.name: Lara Croft (LoRA SDXL 1.0)
items.description:
This LoRA has been trained after carefully selecting 46 images, most of them from Tomb Raider movie. All photos have been enhanced to make the most of them.

When downloading model and testing it, try to copy any of the prompts I have used, and make some variations in order to get other images you prefer. Have fun!

There is a great range of improvement in base model, especially regarding weird limbs or hands (yes, it's still there!! :( ) Anyway I'm satisfied with this model, waiting for future improved photorealistic checkpoints based on SDXL base 1.0.

LoRA weights should be between 1.1 and 1.4 in my experience (but you're free to test)

For portraits you can use 896 x 1152, 768 x 1344, 832 x 1216, 640 x 1536 or even 768x1024 resolutions.

I don't ask for anything but any respectful constructive review (after having tested the model) would be highly appreciated or at least press Like if you're happy with results after trying it out! Thanks in advance and enjoy it!

Notice: This free work is intended for art and illustration purposes of emergent technology and not intended nor' trained for making illicit images, as the author I've taken care to not use any private data in the training process or designed it for such purposes. By downloading this model you are agreeing with the aforementioned intent and that you will not use my work to create / share images of a potentially immoral and / or illegal nature.

items.name: yuuka/早瀬ユウカ/优香 (Blue Archive)
items.description:
NOTE: ALL CHARACTERS IN THE IMAGES ARE ADULTS.

How to Use This Model

USE THEM SIMULTANEOUSLY. In this case, you need to download both yuuka_bluearchive.pt and yuuka_bluearchive.safetensors, then use yuuka_bluearchive.pt as texture inversion embedding, and use yuuka_bluearchive.safetensors as LoRA at the same time.

それらを同時に使用してください。この場合、yuuka_bluearchive.ptとyuuka_bluearchive.safetensorsの両方をダウンロード する必要があります。yuuka_bluearchive.ptをテクスチャ反転埋め込みとして使用し、同時にyuuka_bluearchive.safetensorsをLoRAとして使用してください。

同时使用它们。在这种情况下，您需要下载yuuka_bluearchive.pt和yuuka_bluearchive.safetensors这两个文件，然后将yuuka_bluearchive.pt用作纹理反转嵌入， 同时使用yuuka_bluearchive.safetensors作为LoRA。

(Translated with ChatGPT)

The trigger word is yuuka_bluearchive, and the recommended tags are masterpiece, best quality, highres, solo, {yuuka_bluearchive:1.10}, long_hair, halo, bangs, purple_hair, blush, breasts, purple_eyes, blue_eyes, two_side_up, id_card, thighs, medium_breasts, sticker_on_face.

How This Model Is Trained

This model is trained with HCP-Diffusion. And the auto-training framework is maintained by DeepGHS Team.

Why Some Preview Images Not Look Like Yuuka Bluearchive

All the prompt texts used on the preview images (which can be viewed by clicking on the images) are automatically generated using clustering algorithms based on feature information extracted from the training dataset. The seed used during image generation is also randomly generated, and the images have not undergone any selection or modification. As a result, there is a possibility of the mentioned issues occurring.

In practice, based on our internal testing, most models that experience such issues perform better in actual usage than what is seen in the preview images. The only thing you may need to do is fine-tune the tags you use.

I Felt This Model May Be Overfitting or Underfitting, What Shall I Do

Our model has been published on huggingface repository - CyberHarem/yuuka_bluearchive, where models of all the steps are saved. Also, we published the training dataset on huggingface dataset - CyberHarem/yuuka_bluearchive, which may be help to you.

Why Not Just Using The Better-Selected Images

Our model's entire process, from data crawling, training, to generating preview images and publishing, is 100% automated without any human intervention. It's an interesting experiment conducted by our team, and for this purpose, we have developed a complete set of software infrastructure, including data filtering, automatic training, and automated publishing. Therefore, if possible, we would appreciate more feedback or suggestions as they are highly valuable to us.

Rodrigo Gomes Simoni


Rodrigo Gomes Simoni, better known as Rodrigão, is a youtuber who runs the Adriana e Rodrigão channel alongside his wife.

Recommended

Sampling method: Euler A (But you can use another one of your choice).
CFG Scale: 5 ~ 8 (For photorealism make it 6~5 or less, for 3D blends make it 7~8 or more)

RECOMMENDATIONS :-
Use LoRA name according to the downloaded file when copying example prompts.

  1. Highres Fix - If you are getting blurry and ugly images & try reducing LoRA weight

    My upscale method: txt2img 512x768 -> send to img2img -> controlnet tile upscale, tile diffusion 2x scale with 4xUltrasharp upscaler and tiled vae

  2. Weight: 0.6 - 0.7

  3. Clip Skip: 2

  4. Denoising - Don't go too high, it can alter a lot of details

  5. For better face's - you can use ADetailer

There are imperfections here & there, which i usually leave it in as is, (i never do any inpainting in examples), most of which like hands can be fixed with better prompting, negative embeddings while other like weapons are just bad majority of the time no matter the model as of today.

items.name: NutellaVO
items.description:
Nutella was a model who was starred on the adult site virginoff. She has now retired but you can still find pictures of her online.

To use this lora, simply add "nutellavo" as a trigger word and the lora at suggested weight 1.0.

This lora was trained on 130 pictures of her, some full body shots, some really close. All were 512 by 512 so that is the best resolution to work with. Some backgrounds may appear by default if you don't choose them by yourself.

Many pictures showed her partially or totally naked, so include some clothing description in your prompt to avoid getting nsfw images.

She also tends to tilt her head when facing the viewer. If you don't want that, try adding "head tilt" to the negative prompt.

Example pictures were all generated on RealisticVisionsV5.1, 26 sampling steps with DPM++ 2M Karras with a 512x512 resolution. I then did img2img with same prompt and settings to get an upscale to 1024. Cropping was done at this step when choosing how many pixels the height should be. No other lora or lycoris was used for examples, but it can work well with some I tried.

Although clip skip 2 seems to get better composition than clip skip 1, it tends to undress her a bit more as well. Generate more to get a good seed or add more words in your negative prompt to avoid nsfw pictures if you don't want them.

This is my second trained lora, the first I feel can be shared. Please feel free to ask questions or give me tips for my future projects!

Please share your creations, I'd love to see what you can do with this!

这是群星再世第六十期，以后会不定期出去世的群星Lora，以纪念他们。

罗君左，正是这群人中的一员，说起他的名字，绝大多数人都不认识，但说起鹿清笃，包不同，说不得大师，桑结喇嘛，可能脑海里会立刻想起他的脸庞，在TVB29年里，罗君左出演过97部电视剧，平均一年就有3.3部，可以算是个高产的演员了。能从诸多配角中突出重围，罗君左靠的是自己的实力。罗君左不仅演戏给人留下深刻印象，他的配音功力也堪称一绝，曾经为莫少聪，林志颖等配过音，而《刀剑笑》中林青霞扮演的角色就是由他配音完成的。不止于此，罗君左还非常擅长模仿，曾经在节目中国多次模仿沈殿霞，模仿的程度，真的可以以假乱真了。

这个lora整理的全部都是年轻时的罗君左形象，没有收集罗君左先生得糖尿病后形象变化，以及截肢后的素材，那时的他脸上还是胖胖的。
